Title: Anaconda
Writer: Hans Bauer, Jim Cash, Jack Epps Jr.
Actors: Jennifer Lopez, Ice Cube, Jon Voight, Eric Stoltz
Plot: When a documentary crew traveling through the Amazon jungle, picks up a stranded man, they are unaware of the trouble that will occur. This stranger's hobby is to capture the giant Anaconda snake, and plans to continue targeting it on their boat, by any means necessary.
